ef subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00893">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 24. 2. 1899</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00919">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 29. 5. 1899</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
